Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两周前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.58,0:00:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个隐形穹顶罩住了切斯特磨坊镇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使我们与世隔绝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么穹顶会在这里  以后还会有什么谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们依然一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天它都考验我们的极限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.96,0:00:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激发我们内心最善和最恶一面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.34,0:00:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人说我们会永远困在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.09,0:00:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们会一直奋力寻找出路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得莱尔就是消失在这里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詹姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.35,0:00:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.52,0:00:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈让你相信莱尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.50,0:00:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说在她死前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两天前  她给我发了一封电邮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在外面的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.09,0:00:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我梦里看见过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也看过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的家乡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,齐尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是从那里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直说你站在我这边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.61,0:00:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你肯定对我心怀不满
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.43,0:00:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀了你侄子爱过的一个19岁的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波琳写进日记里的一切都成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:00:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面写着如果那四个小孩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:00:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹顶就会落下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不许碰那些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做噩梦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.99,0:01:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山姆跳下了悬崖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没法阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跳崖之前也这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.22,0:01:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他承认杀了安琪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他认为他死去妹妹的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于安琪和手的画作就像是某种信息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他杀了他们  穹顶就会落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要休息会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.38,0:01:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天一早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.33,0:01:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得去告诉小詹姆斯和乔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你累了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不累吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.85,0:02:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一想到莱尔还逍遥法外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要杀我们  就睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.55,0:02:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你熬夜来保护我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不难
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.95,0:02:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正乔的鼾声就像发情的大象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚这颗蛋还做了什么其它事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展示给我们齐尼斯的方尖塔之后就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么它会把我家乡的东西展示给我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的家乡就是芭比的家乡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定意味着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘  有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是友军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你成功从塌方中出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你安然无恙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到了蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在湖中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我们聚在一起的时候  它浮上了湖面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它需要和我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得保护它的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得谈谈山姆的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我舅舅还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他死了  小詹姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天  你和山姆去隧道找莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为我们以为莱尔杀了安琪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是山姆干的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了她在他身上留下的抓痕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道真相后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就跳下了隧道尽头的悬崖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很遗憾  小詹姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我难道要相信你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不了解我舅舅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要去追他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要找到山姆的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拥有的唯一确凿证据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是安琪在他身上留下的抓痕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有小詹姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和镇民看到证据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事才算了结
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来你又挺过了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备告诉你我在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是让我继续猜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  芭比
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我迟早会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  我昨天在隧道遇到麻烦的原因是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在探索隧道时没有装备齐全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式探索一下  看看下面有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会告诉我你的发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会第一个告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失在了黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山姆也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没听到落地声  这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟穹顶一样古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得悬崖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能通向哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激光笔射不到另一侧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更怪的是  我的指南针在旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎所有方向都聚集在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜欢这情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不喜欢  但你看到了小詹姆斯的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会相信山姆杀了安琪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非他看到尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓痕什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向我保证你会小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形容一下岩壁  有植被吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么活物也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在应该下来了20英尺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到崖底吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这黑暗  我好像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离得越来越近了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你们动了缆绳吗  -不  我们没动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  刚有东西吸引了我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比  上来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐  固定锚要掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉亚  坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽贝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比  我抓住绳子了  你得爬上来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉亚  放手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉亚  松开绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉亚  我坚持不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不松手  我们也会掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比  不准这样  我拉住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我爱你  茱莉亚  -我可以拉你上来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}穹顶之下  第二季第七集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比  你能听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比  说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-茱莉亚  -芭比
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比  说话啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-别这样  来来  过来  -说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得是他干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前认识我舅舅  就在你...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前活着的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他会杀人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前认识的山姆和蔼可亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是一副笑眯眯的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在我也不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他内心还有非常黑暗的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前信任他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己的舅舅怎么会杀安琪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山姆杀的安琪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比  他们一起在隧道里的时候芭比发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后山姆就自杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是芭比告诉你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你遗憾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先去楼下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你很难受  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你舅舅他一直...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他格格不入
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们才一直合不来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不像我跟你这么坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们镇需要力量  需要我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我才不关心我们镇需要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得关心  现在尤其得关心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很特殊  小詹姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹顶选择了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你又是我儿子...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了  你这些话我听够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小詹姆斯  小詹姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小詹姆斯  你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么非把一切扯到你身上去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安琪很喜欢这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她永远不会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从中走出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远都无法走出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我必须接受这个现实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你盯着这个看得出神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像它是个水晶球一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它让我想到了穹顶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事说不通
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么事能说通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前那里没有隧道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在却有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:11:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思  乔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隧道是哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该再回去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都已经喊过他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没有任何回应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从那么高的地方跌下去  没有生还可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  要不你先躺下休息休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的贮藏室里有张沙发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽贝卡  不能让别人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等我去告诉大家这个消息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我得先想清楚怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是担心大个儿吉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比不在了  指不定他会做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听你的  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山姆的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是听小詹姆斯说的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道后很崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干什么  吉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟芭比谈谈  他在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正在  找山姆的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我刚好去帮他一把
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隧道里不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时都有可能坍塌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽贝卡让我也上来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  茱莉亚  心烦意乱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  是因为土
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像她说的  那下面环境很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且只有芭比才有设备能下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想问问你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能去一下警局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以免有人打进电话来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  只要能帮上忙我什么都能做
