Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想找波琳·维多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她哥哥  山姆·维多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找人带你上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"带我上去"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妹妹在隔离病房
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我需要一名陪同人员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比不见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他故意割断了绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不让丽贝卡和我掉到悬崖下面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不相信  茱莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹顶不会让芭比出事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大个儿吉姆想要绞死他的时候穹顶发作了  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三周前还没有的隧道现在突然就冒出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫三周前还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都住在切斯特磨坊镇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校下面的地下室一直都只是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在会出现一条隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是穹顶挖的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那条隧道  悬崖以及芭比掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会都是穹顶的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么计划
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们可以弄明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们能到悬崖下面去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会让你那么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一定要我们去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是学校机器人社团的主席
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做的东西可能会帮我们弄明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那悬崖下面是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  半个小时后在储物柜那见面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妹妹在这里很久了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间基本没什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}艺术疗法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也提醒一下你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你们的视觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是在穹顶里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-穹顶落下了吗  -没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想弄明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小詹姆斯呢  他出来了吗  他没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还在切斯特磨坊镇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他收到了你的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有太多要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别费劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道邻居会有多吵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们要谈的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别人不需要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉姆  你在这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的  我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某种程度上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这件事责怪自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我信过你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不该信的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你惹了我  是大错特错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我难道没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹顶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从绞架上  救了我一命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它救赎了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择了我  来帮它做事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你却不明白  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不用骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉姆  你吓到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你就该害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我守在那学校外面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你走了  但芭比呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许再骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:22:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回家  芭比
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.42,0:23:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是很担心你  芭比
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守在你公寓外面监视
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.80,0:23:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你过去三周躲哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.86,0:23:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里克
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.34,0:23:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你答应我了你要去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.02,0:23:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替玛克辛办点差事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.90,0:23:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就回来帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.63,0:23:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被耽搁了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.41,0:23:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你清楚我们要弄到阿克泰昂能源
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.26,0:23:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研发部门的那份资料
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那会让大家都发财的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.42,0:23:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你肯定会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你却突然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会相信我说...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.78,0:23:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被困在穹顶里面了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.34,0:23:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要完成答应的阿克泰昂的活儿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.45,0:23:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报酬减半
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:23:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不答应呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你嘴里剩的牙齿说不出这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.12,0:24:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.50,0:24:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过...  给我一天时间准备  行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.34,0:24:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才回来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.20,0:24:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.35,0:24:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是不敢相信你出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.55,0:24:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.43,0:24:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在学校底下发现了隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.91,0:24:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隧道尽头  有个悬崖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.15,0:24:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.33,0:24:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跳下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.55,0:24:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-故意跳的吗  -不
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.57,0:24:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隧道很黑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.94,0:24:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.89,0:24:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.34,0:24:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.57,0:24:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还找到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.33,0:24:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.40,0:24:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备假装去世
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.90,0:24:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不相信我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.77,0:24:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.57,0:24:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不告诉你是因为我不相信我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.54,0:24:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.04,0:25:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算大个儿吉姆说我疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.00,0:25:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道穹顶会降下来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.31,0:25:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你没疯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.70,0:25:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹顶的确降下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.47,0:25:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我觉得如果离开切斯特磨坊镇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.12,0:25:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹顶就会跟我走的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.42,0:25:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很怕告诉你我的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.27,0:25:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你肯定会阻止我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.50,0:25:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.90,0:25:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我怀疑过你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.49,0:25:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常人都会的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.73,0:25:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱尔这疯子信我也不奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.43,0:25:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才找他帮你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.71,0:25:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去这些年我给他寄明信片
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.59,0:25:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这么利用他不对
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.17,0:25:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我得跟别人保持联系
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.73,0:25:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也清楚他不会跟别人说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.11,0:25:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这么做是为了拯救小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.12,0:25:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.38,0:25:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我错了  而现在
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.47,0:25:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詹姆斯还困在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.45,0:25:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你和莱尔都出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.60,0:25:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜这还是有可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.36,0:25:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.99,0:26:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见过莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.21,0:26:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  我见过他
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.49,0:26:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.58,0:26:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.58,0:26:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.93,0:26:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.62,0:26:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  收到画面了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.32,0:26:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时还在录像
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.45,0:26:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它马上就能让我们看到
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.79,0:26:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个悬崖底部是什么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.57,0:26:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉亚  你确定想要看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.31,0:26:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论底下有什么  我都想看
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.97,0:26:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.15,0:26:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.46,0:26:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  刚下到六米
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.22,0:26:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.71,0:26:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是石头
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.22,0:26:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别的什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.83,0:26:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们失去画面了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.36,0:26:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不应该啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.76,0:27:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.46,0:27:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.36,0:27:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好让它飞回来  乔  让它上来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.38,0:27:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在努力  但它就是不上来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.64,0:27:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明说过你知道怎么操纵它
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.91,0:27:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.44,0:27:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.88,0:27:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去信号了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.56,0:27:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  茱莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.77,0:27:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我自己的错
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.20,0:27:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你们提起发现了隧道时
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.99,0:27:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很想
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.30,0:27:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要相信有可能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.99,0:27:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.23,0:27:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计们
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.71,0:27:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们得看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.77,0:28:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得刚才闪光中好像有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.00,0:28:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我倒回了视频
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.94,0:28:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有闪光  然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.07,0:28:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要一帧一帧看才行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.89,0:28:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.02,0:28:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来像个滑梯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.67,0:28:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我觉得是个小游乐场
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.13,0:28:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.97,0:28:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.82,0:28:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.39,0:28:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是方尖塔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.77,0:29:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是这个地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.28,0:29:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿克泰昂能源的老板就住在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.16,0:29:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上你的嘴  注意身后
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.09,0:29:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.79,0:29:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个贱人敢背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.31,0:29:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下你们的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.92,0:29:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢点  别紧张  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.59,0:29:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我解释
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.37,0:29:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴尔
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.31,0:29:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.13,0:29:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  真的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.62,0:29:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.97,0:29:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝一杯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.88,0:29:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来杯啤酒  如果你有的话
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.64,0:30:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多长时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.83,0:30:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两年吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.47,0:30:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两年半
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.70,0:30:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说  都太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.94,0:30:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-请坐  -不用
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.35,0:30:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我站着就好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.24,0:30:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然开始想念你的固执  是不是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.98,0:30:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我想起你的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.79,0:30:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让别人想起她  我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.43,0:30:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.09,0:30:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你输入了应急密码  然后
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.44,0:30:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒了你的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.21,0:30:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这无关紧要  他已经被抓起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.02,0:30:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你也不会告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.26,0:30:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些伤是怎么来的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.06,0:30:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你来不是为了跟我增进感情的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.47,0:30:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.65,0:31:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.06,0:31:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅兰妮
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.32,0:31:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅兰妮
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.93,0:31:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直在重复叫这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.57,0:31:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察在镇子中心找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.20,0:31:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-看着方尖塔  -梅兰妮
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.78,0:31:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把他带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.48,0:31:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅兰妮  梅兰妮
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.06,0:31:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.25,0:31:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅兰妮
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.99,0:31:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅兰妮
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.69,0:31:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱尔  能听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.29,0:31:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.31,0:31:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅兰妮
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.76,0:31:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也认不出我了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.76,0:31:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在只会吃饭  睡觉  呼叫梅兰妮
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.26,0:31:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人知道他曾经在穹顶里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.78,0:31:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅兰妮
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.07,0:31:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至没人知道他的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.48,0:31:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他身上也没钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.90,0:31:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他掉下悬崖之后
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.00,0:31:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.27,0:31:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.00,0:31:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.19,0:32:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅兰妮
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.78,0:32:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅兰妮
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.34,0:32:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说的这个
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.46,0:32:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅兰妮  我只能想到一个人叫这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.40,0:32:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不可能是在说她吧  对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.33,0:32:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认识的梅兰妮
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.39,0:32:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是多久之前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.08,0:32:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事应该告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.72,0:32:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅兰妮还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.05,0:32:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她死而复生了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.98,0:32:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你把我弄进穹顶
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.06,0:32:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我把你弄进穹顶
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.09,0:32:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要给里面的一个人传个消息
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.51,0:32:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.08,0:32:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.07,0:32:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然很重要  不然你为什么会来这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.45,0:32:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.99,0:32:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不重要  我是不会来求你的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.29,0:32:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴尔  穹顶的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.52,0:33:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是历史上最重要的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.01,0:33:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全世界都在关注这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.78,0:33:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国民警卫队在穹顶周围设置了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.67,0:33:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,16公里的禁入区
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.22,0:33:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而另外一半则是被炸毁的荒原
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.95,0:33:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你以前托过关系
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.41,0:33:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.15,0:33:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能就这么去找特区的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.11,0:33:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.67,0:33:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会觉得我是个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.76,0:33:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以对你来说这是个生意
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.13,0:33:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.82,0:33:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你一点都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.93,0:33:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做的每一次生意都是为了家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.00,0:33:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你永远都意识不到这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.85,0:33:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你意识到了  就不会出走参军了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.26,0:33:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不用在你被分配部署之前
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.27,0:33:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托关系把你带回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.98,0:33:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没求你这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.53,0:33:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.34,0:33:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你妈妈求了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.21,0:34:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得你回家之后
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.85,0:34:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就生病了只是个巧合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.46,0:34:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她知道她不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.63,0:34:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只想和你道别
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.19,0:34:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  我从没有
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.79,0:34:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求过你任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.94,0:34:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在我求你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.68,0:34:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.85,0:34:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我弄进穹顶
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.41,0:34:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.39,0:34:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺莉
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.64,0:34:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一定在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.87,0:34:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其它地方我们都找遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.56,0:34:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.64,0:34:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.30,0:35:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜欢待在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.22,0:35:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.43,0:35:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.81,0:35:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.22,0:35:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.90,0:35:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我们吓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.28,0:35:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们听说了芭比的事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.60,0:35:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.94,0:35:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  但情况很复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.47,0:35:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉亚在下面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.09,0:35:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.22,0:35:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.61,0:35:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  你们带了蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.65,0:35:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.63,0:35:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时机正好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.89,0:35:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  我们得给你们看一样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.81,0:35:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.46,0:36:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.65,0:36:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在举行追悼会
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.77,0:36:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追悼芭比
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.75,0:36:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉亚不该在场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.86,0:36:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人能找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.91,0:36:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想等了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.75,0:36:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为芭比对这座小镇很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.28,0:36:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他走了我很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.46,0:36:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我们有时是敌人  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.69,0:36:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他通常是唯一一个
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.26,0:36:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站在这座小镇和灾难之间的人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.50,0:36:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对大家而言都是个损失
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.20,0:36:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们该聚在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.75,0:36:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.28,0:37:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得该做祈祷了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.98,0:37:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.79,0:37:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们站拢一点
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.64,0:37:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请低头
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.23,0:37:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天父
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.92,0:37:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前帮我们渡过黑暗的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.91,0:37:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.89,0:37:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会帮我们挺过这次灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.14,0:37:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴你决定留下来  戴尔
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.72,0:37:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就今晚
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.77,0:37:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我欠你真相
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.64,0:37:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么真相
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.48,0:37:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么想进穹顶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.99,0:37:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算大胆推测一下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.01,0:37:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.32,0:37:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.41,0:37:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道你不是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.36,0:37:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我两年半之前熟悉的那个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.15,0:37:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说  你改变了  戴尔
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.53,0:38:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你控制自己
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.46,0:38:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.04,0:38:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从伊拉克
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.40,0:38:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带回来的锋芒已经不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.52,0:38:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道只有一样东西能做到那点
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.34,0:38:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.90,0:38:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.63,0:38:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爱她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.73,0:38:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我爱她
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.14,0:38:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白我们在冒很大的风险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.77,0:38:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.24,0:38:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意冒险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.53,0:38:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.33,0:38:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.51,0:38:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你进穹顶
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.14,0:38:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.57,0:38:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白和自己心爱的女人分开
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.77,0:38:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.78,0:38:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.30,0:39:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.00,0:39:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的觉得乔有所发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.44,0:39:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.34,0:39:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我希望如此
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.61,0:39:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.54,0:39:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它又在发光了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.52,0:39:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.02,0:39:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
